nodes.text: A male individual served Prince-Admiral Delak Krennel in the naval forces of the Ciutric Hegemony as a captain of the Victory-class Star Destroyer Aspiration. After the Battle of Distna, his ship was sent to check the site of the battle for any survivors. There, he noticed a Star Destroyer, but did not detain it, believing it to be one of Krennel's ships.
